NT START--><span style="color:yellow;">This story takes place at the beginning of the formation of the guild. This would be set aprox 20 years ago game time. I am freely hijacking people for this along the way. If you are not hijacked, it’s more than likely Aaldari did not know you at the time the story takes place. Feel free to add on to it if you like. However, I ask that you do not change Aaldari’s place until she reaches Halas (you will understand as the story goes on) the plot is very set until that point. Other than that, feel free to add on with your character or make up ones if you wish. BTW unless they are guilded people or good friends of mine, the names are made up. Any resemblance to living people or avatars is purely coincidental, blah blah blah.</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <br>
